  <Overview>Modern web-based scan server for network and USB scanners. Control scanners remotely and route documents to SMB shares, email, cloud storage, or webhooks.

Features:
- Auto-Discovery for USB and network scanners (SANE/eSCL)
- 9 Target Types: SMB, SFTP, Email, Paperless-ngx, Webhooks, Google Drive, Dropbox, OneDrive, Nextcloud
- Multi-Language support (English/German)
- Statistics dashboard with comprehensive analytics
- Secure encrypted credentials (Fernet AES-128)
- Auto-Retry for failed uploads
- PWA support - Install as native app
- Real-Time WebSocket updates

Default Login: admin / admin (change immediately!)

IMPORTANT: Host network mode is required for scanner discovery (mDNS/Avahi)</Overview>
